  "title": "E-commence Asst",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Responsibiliites:-</strong></u></p><ul><li>Assist with the conceptualisation and execution of e-commerce marketing campaigns across our online platforms.</li><li>To analyze and report online sales KPIs (sales, conversion, traffic, etc)</li><li>To manage order fulfillment.</li><li>Handle customer enquires via various platform.</li><li>Design, update and manage content of all online platforms and ensure that product content, images, inventory, promotion mechanics and pricing are updated timely.</li><li>Provide administrative and operations support to e-commerce team.</li><li>Support the team with ad-hoc duties.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:-</strong></u></p><ul><li>Possess at least a Diploma in the field of marketing, business, e-commerce or related field.</li><li>Proficient in the use of photoshop and/or illustrator.</li><li>Experience in electronics products and e-commerce background will be an added bonus.</li><li>Team player with good communication skills.</li></ul><p>Mon-Fri, 8.45am to 5.30pm</p>",
